    "See [26, Theorem 6.5, page 162].",
    "We remark that since A generates a semigroup of contractions, continuity of paths follows from the continuity of paths of the stochastic convolution, see [26, Theorem 6.2, page 159] or [52, Theorem 1.112 ].",
